        <abstract>
            <p>Thanks WO for advice and assistance for his son, Horace.</p> 
<p>Has read Kerner’s book [see <hi rend="doubleUnderline">11666</hi>]; finds the translation "as clear as daylight" but fears it is too good for the English public who like "very washy food".</p> 
        </abstract>
